form.steps-form(name="verify", validate)
	p.lead.pack Verify invite code

	p.text-center.steps.large
		span.icon-unread.active
		span.icon-unread
		span.icon-unread
		span.icon-unread
		span.icon-unread
		span.icon-unread

	span.error(ng-bind="currentErrorMessage")

	div.form-group
		input.form-control.input-lg(type='text', ng-model='form.username', placeholder="your username", minlength=4, required)
	div.form-group
		textarea.form-control.input-lg(type='text', ng-model='form.token', placeholder="please paste invite code here", minlength=16, required)

	hr.spacer

	.checkbox
		input#check1(type='checkbox', value='check1')
		label(for='check1') I want to be the first to hear about Lavaboom news, send me the latest form.Lava HQ

	p.text-center 
		span By signing up I've agreed that I've read and understood the 
		a Terms of Service and the Privacy Policy

	footer
		button.btn.btn-block.btn-lg.btn-primary(type='submit', ng-disabled='verify.$invalid', ng-click='verifyInvite()') Next Step